e beauty industry and are dedicated to supplying their customers/consumers the latest in beauty and lifestyle products in a convenient and timely fashion.\n\n<strong>THE ROLE</strong>\n\nYou will be approaching beauty companies (warm leads and previous partners) on a daily business, mainly through the mediums of email, face-to-face meetings and networking events. There will also be sales conducted over the phone but this will be a smaller part of the role.\n\nThe chosen candidate for this role will be extremely proactive, self-motivated and driven by success and financial reward. You will be working alongside the Head of Sales who will give you everything you need to be a success. As the sales team will consist solely of the two of you, the opportunity to capitalise on a huge bank of leads will see that you can make a huge amount of sales and commission.\n\nRelationships building/maintaining is a huge part of this role. This means rigid diary management so as to check in with clients at timely intervals throughout the year, keeping updated with product launches and events etc.\n\nYou MUST have target driven sales experience as this will be a fast-paced, sales focussed role.\n\n<strong>THE PERKS</strong>\n\nThis brand have metropolitan offices in Berlin, Stockholm, London, Paris and New York which means there is opportunity for international travel.\n\nYou will often receive free products through your work and on Mondays the office receives a free Personal Training session.\n\nThe office is a fun, friendly environment and you are rewarded and applauded for the hard work you put in!\n\nIf this is something you’re interested in, apply ASAP as interviews are immediately available.','Brand Sales Manager - Beauty Product Sales','','trash','closed','closed','','brand-sales-manager-beauty-product-sales__trashed','','','2017-12-31 14:45:33','2017-12-31 14:45:33','',0,'',14,'iwj_job','',0),(2164,1,'2018-01-03 17:16:09','2018-01-03 17:16:09','{\n    \"show_on_front\": {\n     