 years Native iOS development experience</li>\n 	<li>Published apps on the App Store</li>\n 	<li>Strong iOS UI design principles, patterns and best practices</li>\n 	<li>iOS Ecosystem and libraries</li>\n 	<li>REST/WCF Services</li>\n 	<li>Cloud Message API\'s</li>\n 	<li>Git</li>\n 	<li>User Interfaces such as Touch or Haptic</li>\n 	<li>Offline storage, threading and Performance tuning.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>The Company</strong>\n\nThis company is a leading supplier of infrastructure and software solutions to the healthcare and Public Sector. They are based in Sutton Coldfield, West Midlands and are growing at a rapid rate.\n\nIf you are a passionate iOS Developer and want to be a part of this amazing company and take your iOS experience to the next level then please send me your CV today to or call me on\n\n<strong>iOS Developer - iOS, Git, API - Sutton Coldfield - Up to £40,000\n</strong>\n\nOscar Technology Limited is acting as an Employment Agency in relation to this vacancy.','iOS Developer - iOS, Git, API - Sutton Coldfield','','trash','closed','closed','','ios-developer-ios-git-api-sutton-coldfield__trashed','','','2017-12-31 14:45:32','2017-12-31 14:45:32','',0,'',6,'iwj_job','',0),(1215,1,'2017-06-13 09:31:34','2017-06-13 09:31:34','<div class=\"job-desc\">\n<h3>Job Description</h3>\nCurabitur non nulla sit amet nisl tempus convallis quis ac lectus. Mauris blandit aliquet elit, eget tincidunt nibh pulvinar a. Praesent sapien massa, convallis a pellentesque nec, egestas non nisi. Curabitur aliquet quam id dui posuere blandit. Nulla porttitor accumsan tincidunt.\n\nDonec rutrum congue leo eget malesuada. Pellentesque in ipsum id orci porta dapibus. Donec sollicitudin molestie malesuada. Vivamus magna justo, lacinia eget consectetur sed, convallis at tellus. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n<h3>Benefits</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Vestibulum ac diam sit amet quam vehicula elementum sed sit amet dui. Sed porttitor lectus nibh. Pellentesque in ip